name: C2G Velocity - Audio cable - RCA (M) to stereo mini jack (M) - 50 ft - shielded - blue | Dell USA
description: Specifically designed to provide quality music transfer from your PC sound card, portable CD player, MP3 player, iPod, or any mini-stereo audio device to another audio device with RCA audio jacks. This cable features two 27 AWG oxygen-free copper conductors, a drain wire, an aluminum foil shield to prevent unwanted EMI/RFI interference, and fully molded, gold-plated connectors providing strain relief for a quality connection.
